that'll make their hearts throb.

22
00:01:32,725 --> 00:01:33,693
I really can't do that.

23
00:01:35,428 --> 00:01:37,497
{\an8}<i>But they were determined...</i>

24
00:01:37,564 --> 00:01:38,364
{\an8}YUTA KISHI (AGE 23)

25
00:01:38,431 --> 00:01:39,766
{\an8}<i>...to do anything.</i>

26
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:44,370
{\an8}If it's for this role, I will do anything.

27
00:01:44,437 --> 00:01:45,472
{\an8}That's how determined I am.

28
