My brain isn't functioning.

36
00:02:17,637 --> 00:02:22,408
{\an8}<i>However, they were encouraged by
the people who support them.</i>

37
00:02:22,475 --> 00:02:24,010
{\an8}REN NAGASE (AGE 20)

38
00:02:24,077 --> 00:02:24,944
{\an8}That's hot!

39
