48
00:03:19,098 --> 00:03:21,601
2020 IS IN OUR HANDS

49
00:03:24,370 --> 00:03:27,707
<i>A total of more than
70 Johnny's Jr. members perform</i>

50
00:03:28,274 --> 00:03:31,110
<i>in this approximately
two-month-long show.</i>

51
00:03:38,751 --> 00:03:39,786
<i>There is singing.</i>

52
00:03:44,557 --> 00:03:45,525
<i>There is dancing.</i>

53
00:03:48,695 --> 00:03:51,197
<i>The youths mature into entertainers.</i>

54
00:03:51,564 --> 00:03:52,966
<i>This is a stepping stone</i>

55
00:03:53,566 --> 00:03:56,469
<i>that their countless
predecessors have treasured.</i>

56
