<i>through starring in several
drama series and movies. Sho Hirano.</i>

61
00:04:30,803 --> 00:04:34,540
<i>Throughout this year,
Hirano has been moving at top speed.</i>

62
00:04:35,908 --> 00:04:37,610
<i>It's no surprise he looks tired.</i>

63
