258
00:16:23,182 --> 00:16:24,216
{\an8}<i>Yuta Kishi.</i>

259
00:16:27,619 --> 00:16:29,321
{\an8}<i>As they keep rising in popularity,</i>

260
00:16:29,755 --> 00:16:33,993
{\an8}<i>he was calmly reflecting on the past year
