261
00:16:36,528 --> 00:16:40,366
We experienced so many things
for the first time.

262
00:16:40,432 --> 00:16:41,900
We had new experiences

263
00:16:41,967 --> 00:16:44,937
and worked with people
who we never worked with before.

264
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:48,173
Everything was new to us.

265
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,109
Of course, trying new things

266
00:16:50,342 --> 00:16:52,678
sometimes led to discouragement.

267
00:16:52,878 --> 00:16:56,715
And... I would learn new things

268
00:16:56,982 --> 00:16:59,718
and become downhearted.

269
00:16:59,952 --> 00:17:01,420
Everyone feels...

270
00:17:02,621 --> 00:17:04,990
downhearted at times, you know?

271
00:17:05,057 --> 00:17:07,726
Like when I'm invited on a show,

272
00:17:07,793 --> 00:17:10,996
