278
00:17:27,646 --> 00:17:29,782
to be able to work as a group.

279
00:17:30,015 --> 00:17:32,017
But you know...

280
00:17:33,886 --> 00:17:36,121
we can't expect it
to be like this forever.

281
00:17:36,388 --> 00:17:40,626
What we need to do at the moment
is to give everything our best.

282
00:17:41,193 --> 00:17:43,462
We just have to try our best

