00:17:43,962 --> 00:17:46,365
to deliver what is expected of us.

284
00:17:47,199 --> 00:17:48,033
Yeah...

285
00:17:50,769 --> 00:17:55,507
As a group, I hope we can become
the type of people

286
00:17:56,341 --> 00:17:59,678
